<br>
This was NOT started to discuss my previous signature.  Do you see that signature in this thread?  No.  I've chaged it.  Deal.<br>
<br>
This thread was started because a mod (Kaileena) suggested that perhaps a rule must be made that will be universally applied.<br>
<br>
While I know that if a rule is made, then it will be up to the mods to decide what it is.  I just figured that *if* a rule will be made, we should all have some input as to what we think it should be so the mods can at least consider it, rather than continue to whine and bitch about particular signatures and then complain when the mods do finally make such a rule.<br>
<br>
If you do not think there should be any new rule, than that is a valid opinion as well that perhaps the mods want to take into account.  Personally that is my point of view as well.<br>
<br>
BUT...if it just so happens that this board will be declared a &quot;family board&quot;, and some new rule will be made to enforce this vision, then I would like to have at least have been heard before any new rule comes into effect.<br>
